  // The dryrun fid is `<formId>_<fieldUuid>` (or `<formId>__systemfield_X`).
  // Per Ashby DOM contract, the per-field container is
  //   <div class="_fieldEntry_*" data-field-path="<fieldUuid|_systemfield_X>">
